<blockquote><p>Hey, so can the object for the OLED be easily modified to be used with a physical projector (to project, perhaps hdmi out)?</p></blockquote></aside>

<p>no! the OLED object is highly specialised for that kind of displays and only works with the i2c connection. additionally, only text and some simple graphic bars can be displayed.</p>
