      <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
        <p>Did you try the help file ? Help -&gt; library -&gt; community -&gt; tiar -&gt; HW -&gt; OLED128x64nice</p>

<p>Note that with the "nice" version you need to include a single gpio/i2c/config object in your patch (it will config the i2c for all the i2c objects once for all).</p>

<p>I hope it will help.</p>

